The source code repository for this project can be found here:
https://github.com/fbcgulfport/companion-midi-satellite

Full licensing information for Companion MIDI Satellite can be found by running 'satellite-license'
in the terminal or visiting https://github.com/fbcgulfport/companion-midi-satellite/blob/main/LICENSE in a web browser

Any bugs, issues, or feature requests for the Companion MIDI Satellite software should be reported on the project's GitHub:
https://github.com/fbcgulfport/companion-midi-satellite/issues

Companion MIDI Satellite should auto-start on this computer as soon as a viable network connection is detected.

For more information on Companion MIDI Satellite specific commands you can run try running `satellite-help`
